<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Activate Your Yshop Account</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap');

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #7158e2;
      /* A modern purple, feels fresh and trustworthy for e-commerce */
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 30px 40px;
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .email-body p {
      margin: 0 0 15px;
    }

    .otp-code-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .otp-code {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7158e2;
      background-color: #f4f7f6;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      border: 1px dashed #d1cceb;
    }

    .email-footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999999;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }

    .email-footer p {
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to Yshop!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering with Yshop! To complete your activation, please use the One-Time Password (OTP)
        below.</p>
      <div class="otp-code-wrapper">
        <div class="otp-code">
          <%= otp %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>This code is valid for the next <strong>5 minutes</strong>. If you did not initiate this request, you can
        safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Yshop Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Yshop. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>